Analytics Plugin Version 0.2
-------------------------

Google Analytics plugin for VamShop


Installation using composer:

1. Install package from your VamShop root directory (where composer.json located):

composer require vamshop/analytics

2. Activate plugin at Admin - Extensions - Plugins - Analytics


Manual Installation:


1. Download or clone repository http://github.com/vamshop/analytics

2. Copy files from archive analytics-master folder to /app/plugins/Analytics folder

3. Activate plugin at Admin - Extensions - Plugins - Analytics


Configuration
-------------

1. Activate the plugin

2. Enter your Web Propery ID and domain name in Settings -> Site

Requirements
------------

VamShop 3.0 - http://github.com/vamshop/


